_sText:
This map allows for 64 players, although reccomended is 20 due to its small size.

This is just another version of aim_ak-colt, with a second floor resembling short A in de_dust2 going around the map. Otherwise, it is just about the same. There is a small easter egg, although no hints on how to find it are being given :).

Map critics are going to talk about lighting, I know. I can honestly say I've made maps in CS:S for only a few weeks, with previous experience in Condition Zero. I'm still having trouble figuring out good lighting methods.

Enjoy my map, spread it around, and have fun!
